<span>The petition includes the reasonable guidelines for food truck operation that we worked out with Councilwoman Head, the Mayor's office, and numerous other stakeholders. The amount of time a food truck can park will be extended from 30 minutes to 4 hours, the distance it must be from a school, church or restaurant will be decreased from 600 feet (3-5 city blocks) to 50 feet, and parts of the CBD will finally have access to mobile food.</span>
